[
  {
    "text": "♪ instrumental hip hop music ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi, I'm Julia from Privacy Engineering, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "and welcome to \"Explore App Tracking Transparency.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "At Apple, we believe privacy is a fundamental human right.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=16"
  },
  {
    "text": "Part of engineering great privacy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "is giving people choices and control ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "over how their data is used.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "When people have these choices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=27"
  },
  {
    "text": "and understand how their data will be linked or shared, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "they are more likely to trust and engage with your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's why, beginning last year, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Store policy requires apps to receive users' permission ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "before tracking users across apps and websites ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "owned by other companies by adopting ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "the AppTrackingTransparency framework.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, I'm going to talk to you about when and how to adopt ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=51"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Tracking Transparency.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, I'll start with some background on tracking ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help you understand if and when your app needs to adopt ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=59"
  },
  {
    "text": "the AppTrackingTransparency framework.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, I'll highlight some key things to keep in mind ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=65"
  },
  {
    "text": "when adopting the framework in practice.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's get started with some background on tracking.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, how is tracking defined for App Tracking Transparency? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tracking refers to linking user or device data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "collected from your app with user or device data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "collected from other companies' apps, websites, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "or offline properties for targeted advertising ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "or advertising-measurement purposes.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tracking also refers to sharing user or device data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "with data brokers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's talk through some example scenarios ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "to better understand how tracking is defined.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, let's look at an advertising scenario ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "that doesn't involve tracking.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "Suppose I download an app called Pal About, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the Pal About app has a feature ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "that lets me search for places and events ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "that are happening nearby.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now suppose I use Pal About to search for places ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "that serve waffles near me, which results in Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "storing waffles as an interest of mine.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "Pal About later wants to show an ad for breakfast places ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "targeting people who like breakfast foods.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "Using the data Pal About stores about me from my searches, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "Pal About shows me the breakfast ad.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=137"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this example, Pal About doesn't link my data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "with any data from an app or website ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "owned by another company to show me the breakfast ad, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=146"
  },
  {
    "text": "so this scenario would not be considered tracking.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=149"
  },
  {
    "text": "For another example that wouldn't be considered tracking, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "suppose the company that owns Pal About -- Pal About Inc. -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=157"
  },
  {
    "text": "has another app that I use called Pal About Plus.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=160"
  },
  {
    "text": "And Pal About's server links together data collected about me ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=164"
  },
  {
    "text": "in Pal About Plus, like my interest in tacos, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "with data collected about me in Pal About.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "After linking this data, Pal About shows me an ad ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "for a taco truck using the fact I like tacos ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "collected from Pal About Plus.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this example, the Pal About app doesn't need ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=184"
  },
  {
    "text": "to get my permission to track because it isn't tracking.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "Pal About doesn't link my data from Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "with any data from an app or website ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "owned by another company.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=195"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's now consider a scenario that would require Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "to get permission to track.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "Suppose there's a food delivery app I use ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "that's owned by a different company than Pal About.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "And I've used the food delivery app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "to place orders late at night.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I signed up for the food delivery app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "I gave the app my email address -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "the same email address I used to sign up for Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "and that Pal About stores for my account.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=221"
  },
  {
    "text": "The food delivery app includes code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "that shares my email address ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the fact I often order at night with Pal About.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "The Pal About server uses my email address to link together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "my interest in waffles, collected by the Pal About app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the fact I order at night, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "collected in the food delivery app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, Pal About uses the combination ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "of my ordering habits and my interest in waffles ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "to show me an ad for a restaurant ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=250"
  },
  {
    "text": "that serves all-day breakfast.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=252"
  },
  {
    "text": "This scenario would require Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "to request permission to track ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=257"
  },
  {
    "text": "because it linked user data from Pal About -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "my email address -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "with another company's user data -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=263"
  },
  {
    "text": "my email and habit of ordering at night -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "for advertising purposes.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this example, data is linked together across apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=270"
  },
  {
    "text": "with an email address.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "Even if the email address or another user identifier ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "is hashed before it is used to link data, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=279"
  },
  {
    "text": "it would still require permission to track ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "because it would still be linking data about a user ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the app with another company's data about that user.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "The type of identifier and whether or not it is hashed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "doesn't change the fact it is being used for tracking, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=296"
  },
  {
    "text": "which is what requires permission.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "Another thing you'll need to consider ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "to determine if your app needs to request permission to track ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "is how third-party SDKs use and share data from your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=308"
  },
  {
    "text": "As a developer, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're responsible for the behavior of your whole app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=313"
  },
  {
    "text": "Returning to our example, suppose the Pal About developer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=317"
  },
  {
    "text": "hasn't written any code themselves ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "that would require permission to track, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=323"
  },
  {
    "text": "but would like to include a third-party SDK in their app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "for advertising-measurement purposes.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=328"
  },
  {
    "text": "Whether Pal About needs permission to track ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=331"
  },
  {
    "text": "in order to include the SDK depends on whether or not ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=333"
  },
  {
    "text": "the SDK combines user data from Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "with user data from other companies' apps or websites.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, if the SDK shares user data from Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "to provide analytics about ads in Pal About, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=349"
  },
  {
    "text": "but doesn't link the user data it collects from Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "with user data from other companies, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=355"
  },
  {
    "text": "it doesn't require permission to track.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now suppose instead, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=362"
  },
  {
    "text": "the SDK shares user data from Pal About with an ad network, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=364"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the ad network links the data it receives ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "about how I use Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=372"
  },
  {
    "text": "with data about ads I saw in other companies' apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "to compare the impact of ad campaigns in those apps.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=376"
  },
  {
    "text": "This requires Pal About to request users' permission ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "to track because this SDK is tracking.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is considered tracking regardless of whether Pal About ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "uses the SDK for those purposes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=390"
  },
  {
    "text": "or even if Pal About only gets aggregate reporting ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=392"
  },
  {
    "text": "after Pal About users' data is linked ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=396"
  },
  {
    "text": "with other companies' users' data.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're unsure about whether an SDK you want to use ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=402"
  },
  {
    "text": "would contain code that would require ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=405"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Tracking Transparency, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=406"
  },
  {
    "text": "you should ask the developer of that SDK.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "This responsibility applies not just to SDKs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=412"
  },
  {
    "text": "but to any libraries or third-party code your app uses.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=415"
  },
  {
    "text": "So far, we've looked at examples that involve linking user data.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=419"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's look at another scenario ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "that's considered tracking: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=425"
  },
  {
    "text": "sharing user or device data with data brokers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=426"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, how are data brokers defined? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "Data brokers are defined by law in some jurisdictions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=433"
  },
  {
    "text": "But in general, a data broker is a company ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=436"
  },
  {
    "text": "that regularly collects and sells, licenses, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "or otherwise discloses to third parties ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=442"
  },
  {
    "text": "the personal information of particular end users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=445"
  },
  {
    "text": "with whom the business does not have a direct relationship.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=447"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's look at sharing data with a data broker in an example.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=451"
  },
  {
    "text": "Suppose the Pal About app includes client code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "that sends my interest in waffles ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=458"
  },
  {
    "text": "and an account identifier to a data broker.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=460"
  },
  {
    "text": "This scenario counts as tracking ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=464"
  },
  {
    "text": "whether or not the data that is shared ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=466"
  },
  {
    "text": "is linked with data from other companies ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=468"
  },
  {
    "text": "for advertising or advertising measurement.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=470"
  },
  {
    "text": "Sharing of user data with a data broker ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=473"
  },
  {
    "text": "requires permission to track.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=475"
  },
  {
    "text": "And even if Pal About client code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "doesn't directly send my account identifier ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "and my interest in waffles to the data broker, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=484"
  },
  {
    "text": "but instead this interest is sent to Pal About's server ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the server later shares accounts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=490"
  },
  {
    "text": "interested in waffles with the data broker, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=492"
  },
  {
    "text": "this would require getting permission to track ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=495"
  },
  {
    "text": "even though my device isn't communicating ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=497"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the data broker directly.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=500"
  },
  {
    "text": "We've now talked through how the definition of tracking ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=502"
  },
  {
    "text": "applies to some example scenarios.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more information about how App Tracking Transparency ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=507"
  },
  {
    "text": "defines tracking, you can visit ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=510"
  },
  {
    "text": "the User Privacy and Data Use page.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=512"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, if you've determined that your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "would like to track users, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=517"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll need to ask for and obtain the user's permission ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=519"
  },
  {
    "text": "before you do so.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's how.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=523"
  },
  {
    "text": "To ask for permission for your app to track, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll need to present the app tracking authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=528"
  },
  {
    "text": "request prompt by calling ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=531"
  },
  {
    "text": "the requestTrackingAuthorization method.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=533"
  },
  {
    "text": "Calling this method will cause a system permission alert -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "like this one for Pal About -- to appear over your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=540"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a one-time prompt.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=545"
  },
  {
    "text": "The system will remember the user's choice ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=547"
  },
  {
    "text": "and won't prompt again ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=549"
  },
  {
    "text": "unless the app is uninstalled and reinstalled.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=550"
  },
  {
    "text": "The next thing you'll need to do is provide ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=554"
  },
  {
    "text": "a NSUserTrackingUsageDescription key in your app's info.plist.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=557"
  },
  {
    "text": "The string provided here will be shown in the system prompt ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=563"
  },
  {
    "text": "and informs the user why the app is requesting permission ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=566"
  },
  {
    "text": "to use data for tracking the user or the device.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=570"
  },
  {
    "text": "A great purpose string is clear, concise, and helps users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=574"
  },
  {
    "text": "understand why they are being asked to allow tracking.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "This string doesn't need to include the app's name, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=581"
  },
  {
    "text": "because the system will automatically identify ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=584"
  },
  {
    "text": "the requesting app and display the app name ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=586"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the system prompt.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=589"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you don't include a usage-description string, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=591"
  },
  {
    "text": "your app will crash when the system prompt is shown.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=594"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, use trackingAuthorizationStatus ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=597"
  },
  {
    "text": "to determine the user's app-tracking permission status ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=601"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "If a user has selected Allow for this app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=606"
  },
  {
    "text": "then you have their permission to link their activity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "in that app across other apps and websites ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=611"
  },
  {
    "text": "as long as their tracking authorization status ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=614"
  },
  {
    "text": "remains authorized.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=617"
  },
  {
    "text": "Users can change and grant or revoke ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=619"
  },
  {
    "text": "their tracking authorization at any time, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=622"
  },
  {
    "text": "so make sure your app checks the tracking authorization status ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=625"
  },
  {
    "text": "each time it is launched and only continues to track ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=629"
  },
  {
    "text": "when the value of the tracking authorization status ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=632"
  },
  {
    "text": "is authorized.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=635"
  },
  {
    "text": "Users can control whether apps have their permission to track ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=637"
  },
  {
    "text": "on a per-app basis.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=641"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just because a user has given one of your apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=643"
  },
  {
    "text": "permission to track doesn't mean you have their permission ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=646"
  },
  {
    "text": "to track in another app owned by the same company.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=649"
  },
  {
    "text": "Different apps must each individually request permission ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=652"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the user for that particular app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=656"
  },
  {
    "text": "before data from that app can be linked ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=659"
  },
  {
    "text": "to apps or websites owned by other companies ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=661"
  },
  {
    "text": "for marketing or advertising.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=664"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app doesn't have ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=667"
  },
  {
    "text": "tracking authorization for a user, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=669"
  },
  {
    "text": "there are a couple things to keep in mind.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=671"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, per the App Store review guidelines, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=674"
  },
  {
    "text": "your app must not gate any of its functionality ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=677"
  },
  {
    "text": "on whether the user agrees to allow tracking.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=679"
  },
  {
    "text": "Second, the IDFA API will return all zeros ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=683"
  },
  {
    "text": "if the user has asked your app not to track.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=687"
  },
  {
    "text": "If a user has opted out of tracking, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=691"
  },
  {
    "text": "there are nontracking alternatives for advertising ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=693"
  },
  {
    "text": "or advertising measurement for your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=695"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, your app could choose to serve first-party ads ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=698"
  },
  {
    "text": "or contextual ads.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=702"
  },
  {
    "text": "And for advertising measurement, we continue to build and improve ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=703"
  },
  {
    "text": "privacy preserving ad-attribution technologies ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=707"
  },
  {
    "text": "that ad networks can adopt.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=710"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more information about recent improvements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=712"
  },
  {
    "text": "to SKAdNetwork and private click measurement, you can refer to ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=714"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Meet privacy preserving ad attribution\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=718"
  },
  {
    "text": "and \"What's new in SKAdNetwork.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=721"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll also need to declare what data your app uses ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=724"
  },
  {
    "text": "to track for display in your app's privacy nutrition label.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=727"
  },
  {
    "text": "Filling out your privacy nutrition label ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=731"
  },
  {
    "text": "when submitting your app to the App Store ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=733"
  },
  {
    "text": "and getting permission to track using ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=736"
  },
  {
    "text": "the AppTrackingTransparency framework ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=738"
  },
  {
    "text": "are two separate steps that are both required ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=740"
  },
  {
    "text": "if your app would like to use data for tracking.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=743"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more information about nutrition labels ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=746"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how to fill them out for your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=749"
  },
  {
    "text": "see \"Create your Privacy Nutrition Label.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=750"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, let's talk about fingerprinting.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=754"
  },
  {
    "text": "With permission, tracking is allowed.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=757"
  },
  {
    "text": "But fingerprinting is never allowed.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=760"
  },
  {
    "text": "Regardless of whether a user gives your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=763"
  },
  {
    "text": "permission to track, fingerprinting -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=765"
  },
  {
    "text": "or using signals from the device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=768"
  },
  {
    "text": "to try to identify the device or user -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=769"
  },
  {
    "text": "is not allowed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=772"
  },
  {
    "text": "per the Apple Developer Program License Agreement.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=773"
  },
  {
    "text": "Some examples of user or device data used for fingerprinting ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=777"
  },
  {
    "text": "include properties of a user's web browser ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=781"
  },
  {
    "text": "and its configuration, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=783"
  },
  {
    "text": "the user's device and its configuration, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=785"
  },
  {
    "text": "the user's location, or the user's network connection.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=787"
  },
  {
    "text": "Collecting any data solely for the purpose ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=791"
  },
  {
    "text": "of generating a fingerprint is also not allowed.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=794"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's important people have transparency and control ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=798"
  },
  {
    "text": "over how their data is used for tracking.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=800"
  },
  {
    "text": "We hope that by tuning in to this session, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=803"
  },
  {
    "text": "you now have the tools you need to determine ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=806"
  },
  {
    "text": "when and how to give people that control by adopting ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=808"
  },
  {
    "text": "the AppTrackingTransparency framework.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=811"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for watching.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=813"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10166/?time=815"
  }
]